GENERALIZABILITY: ‚≠ê‚≠ê‚≠ê‚òÜ‚òÜ (3/5)
Conducted in retail organization (different from engineering context). 17+ years old (workplace dynamics may have evolved). Voice mechanisms conceptually applicable across settings.

OVERALL CONFIDENCE: 75% (High)

DECISION: ‚úÖ USE THIS EVIDENCE
Rigorous design and rare direct measurement of decision quality. Generalizability moderate but voice dynamics likely similar across contexts.</div>
